[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"html:span","attrib":{},"text":"Oct. 25, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"html:a","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/519/s306/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–519, § 306(a)","children":[],"tail":", (e), "},{"tag":"html:a","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/3397"},"text":"106 Stat. 3397","children":[],"tail":", 3400."}],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In this section, the word “information” is substituted for “data” for consistency in the revised title. The word “standards” is substituted for “standard” because there is more than one standard prescribed under this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (a), before clause (1), the words “","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1995-10-25"},"text":"October 25, 1995","children":[],"tail":"” are substituted for “3 years after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-25"},"text":"October 25, 1992","children":[],"tail":"” (the date of enactment of the Anti-Car Theft Act of 1992) for clarity and to eliminate unnecessary words. In clause (1), the words “distributed for sale in interstate commerce that are” are substituted for “for all such motor vehicles distributed for sale in interstate commerce” for clarity. In clause (5)(A), the word “decrease” is substituted for “have . . . a beneficial impact in decreasing” for consistency and to eliminate unnecessary words."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (b), before clause (1), the words “","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1997-10-25"},"text":"October 25, 1997","children":[],"tail":"” are substituted for “5 years after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-25"},"text":"October 25, 1992","children":[],"tail":"” (the date of enactment of the Anti-Car Theft Act of 1992) for clarity and to eliminate unnecessary words. In clause (1)(B), the word “accuracy” is omitted as redundant. In clause (2), the words “distributed for sale in interstate commerce that are” are substituted for “for all such motor vehicles distributed for sale in interstate commerce” for clarity. In clause (9)(A), the word “decrease” is substituted for “have . . . a beneficial impact in decreasing” for consistency and to eliminate unnecessary words."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (c)(1)(C), the words “carrying out” are substituted for “the implementation, administration, and enforcement” for consistency and to eliminate unnecessary words.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idcb8dde09-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idcb8dde0a-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Motor Vehicle Theft Law Enforcement Act of 1984, referred to in subsecs. (b)(6)(A), (10) and (c)(1)(D), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/547"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–547","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1984-10-25"},"text":"Oct. 25, 1984","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/98/2754"},"text":"98 Stat. 2754","children":[],"tail":". Titles II and III of that act enacted sections 511, 512, 553, and 2320 [now 2321] of Title 18, Crimes and Criminal Procedure, and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s1627"},"text":"section 1627 of Title 19","children":[],"tail":", Customs Duties, and amended sections 1961, 2311, and 2313 of Title 18. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title of 1984 Amendment note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1901"},"text":"section 1901 of Title 15","children":[],"tail":", Commerce and Trade, and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
